      "meaning": "迎击；抵御",
      "examples": [
        "不迓克奔，以役西土。——《书·牧誓》",
        "迓侮，犹言御侮也。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "迓"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "溜走，逃跑",
      "examples": [
